The product features catalog contains a compiled list of all of the features that could be developed and implemented for a product.
This catalog has numerous diagrams that shows the relationship of the features to other features and decomposition to user stories. The purpose of this catalog is to have one place to strategically determine the scope, behavior, dependency on other features for report generation.
The UI Catalogue contain all of the elements that make up the UI. These are uniquely number so they can be assigned to reflect the code elements.
